Register
  Registers new user
  Rejects registration attempt
  Gives reasons why
  Provides neccessary safety level for both user and system
  
Log in
  Authorises by email and password combination
  Rejects autorisation attempt
  Gives reasons why not
  Provides neccessary safety level for both user and system
  
  Keeps the user logged during session
  Keeps the user logged in till he exits